{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "权力帮将唐方、唐朋等人改装押送至客店，祖金殿透露留活口是为了以唐门人质威胁唐老太太，并以欧阳珊一为饵钓马竟终。马竟终潜入客店见妻子后察觉危险逃离，却在死巷中遭左常生和康劫生前后夹击，身中剑伤。与此同时，萧秋水在四川小镇目睹慕容世家的慕容英被权力帮弟子围攻，起因竟是邱南顾在乌江之战时冒称慕容家人所致。慕容英以‘以彼之道还彼之身’的绝技反击，但最终被伪君子康出渔暗剑穿喉杀害。萧秋水怒不可遏，冲出来直面康出渔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "你知道我为什么不杀死你们吗？要劳我们像送老太婆一般护送你们来到这里，嘿！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "你们至今不死，是因为你家世底子好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "蜀中唐家，是李帮主首要消灭的心腹大患，挟持你俩，至少唐本本和唐土土有个顾忌，据说唐门最犀利角色唐老太太还非常疼你，这下实有大用。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "至于这姓欧阳的，大腹便便，我们擒着她，是拿她作饵，来钓那漏网之鱼，她丈夫就在门外，待会儿我们就要收网了，你们信也不信？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "你外号叫做‘落地生根’？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "我叫左常生，外号‘一洞神魔’，你听说过吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "我挖一个洞，正好埋你的根。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_ma_jing_zhong",
      "text": "我叫康劫生，原来是萧秋水的朋友，其实是权力帮的人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhong",
      "text": "我与梁消暑、戚常戚等向无恩怨，几位苦苦相逼，是何意思！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "高中",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "那俺呢？！你看俺是什么人？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhong",
      "text": "我跟彭九也素不相识，无怨无仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "安判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "慕容英，你今日认命便了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "text": "我与诸位，素昧平生……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "安判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "既不相熟，何以又对我们的武功，打探得一清二楚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "text": "我们慕容世家的人，素来对天下任何武术，无一不知。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "这话要是由你们慕容世家的主人慕容世情来说，或者是慕容若容、慕容小意的咀里说出来，都还可以，由你来说，还得要问问我手中的弯刀。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "安判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "慕容英，你别假惺惺，你们慕容家的人要跟权力帮抗衡，别以为我不知道！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "text": "这，这从何说起呢……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "铁判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "慕容英，我问你，你们慕容家有谁是眼小小像粒米，头大大，嘴巴向下撇、鼻子像只钩子带点哨牙儿，讲话出口伤人的家伙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_tie_pan_guan",
      "text": "有这样的人么？我可不知道哇……再说，慕容世家有近五百人，我怎能——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "安判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "不用说了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "铁判官",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "既然你不知，就代他受死吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "text": "我们慕容家没这样的怪人……你们捏造是非来坑人，莫非是南宫世家的人之唆使，或是上官望的门徒出的诡计？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_ting",
      "speaker_name": "康庭",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "南宫世家早已与权力帮合并，上官族早为权力帮所用，你又奈何？！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_kang_ting",
      "text": "没什么奈不奈的，慕容世家屹立江湖三百年，怕过谁来！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_shi",
      "speaker_name": "何狮",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "你别吹了，我们来，主要是找慕容英雄，不是找你，你还不值得我们劳师动众。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_he_shi",
      "text": "英雄哥不但是我们慕容家第五号人物，也是武林中的泰斗，凭你们，还不配去见他！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "高中",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "那你呢？你只配去见阎王爷！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "高中",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "你只配喝我洗脚水。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": "char_gao_zhong",
      "text": "唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小高！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_shi",
      "speaker_name": "何狮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容家‘拂花分柳刺穴法’！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "准？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "来人",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "text": "慕容世侄，是我呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "慕容英",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是前辈……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "康出渔，你这个败类——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18
    }
  ],
